{"questionId":"9070061","questionHtml":"<p>Calculate the specific energy of octane, C<sub>8</sub>H<sub>18</sub>, in kJ kg<sup>–1</sup> using sections 1, 6 and 13 of&nbsp;the data booklet.</p>","markschemeHtml":"<p><em>M</em><sub>r</sub> (C<sub>8</sub>H<sub>18</sub>)&nbsp;= 114.26 <em><strong>AND</strong> </em>Δ<em>H</em><span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"_c^\\theta \">\n  <msubsup>\n    <mi></mi>\n    <mi>c</mi>\n    <mi>θ</mi>\n  </msubsup>\n</math></span><em>=</em>&nbsp;–5470 «kJ mol<sup>–1</sup>»</p>\n<p>«specific energy = <span class=\"mjpage\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" alttext=\"\\frac{{5470\\,{\\text{kJ}}}}{{0.11426\\,{\\text{kg}}}}\">\n  <mfrac>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>5470</mn>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>kJ</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n    <mrow>\n      <mn>0.11426</mn>\n      <mspace width=\"thinmathspace\"></mspace>\n      <mrow>\n        <mtext>kg</mtext>\n      </mrow>\n    </mrow>\n  </mfrac>\n</math></span> =» 4.79&nbsp;x 10<sup>4</sup>/47873/47900 «kJ kg<sup>–1</sup>»</p>\n<p><em>Award <strong>[2]</strong> for correct final answer.</em></p>\n<p><em>Accept “48&nbsp;x 10<sup>3</sup> «kJ kg<sup>–1</sup>»” <strong>OR&nbsp;</strong>“47.9&nbsp;x 10<sup>3</sup> «kJ kg<sup>–1</sup>»”.</em></p>","meta":{"questionId":"9070061","referenceCode":"17N.3.sl.TZ0.a","subjectId":"45-dp-chemistry-last-assessment-2024","title":"Calculate the specific energy of octane, C8H18, in kJ kg–1 using sections 1, 6 and 13 of the data booklet.","paper":"3","level":"sl","questionNumber":"a","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 2]","breadcrumbLabels":["Options","Options","C: Energy","C.1 Energy sources","Options","C: Energy"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}